line_1: She shakes the dice, the board she knocks,
line_2: And from all pockets fills her box.
The sleepless Gout here counts the crowing Cocks,
Down to the Ground at once, as Butcher felleth Ox.

line_1: Now groans the Table with repeated Knocks;
line_2: Now the Dice rattle in the sounding Box;

line_1: HARK! on the wainscote now IT knocks!
line_2: If Thou'rt a Ghost, cried ORTHODOX,
